parameters:
Mage Relm: What is it? Why did you summon me all the way
here?

Researcher Dokusa: It's something difficult to discuss at
the Magic Academy.

Mage Relm: Is it another threat to the world or something?
We're not exactly free, so please get to the point
quickly...
Mage Relm: Is it really an important matter...?
Researcher Dokusa: I want you to take a look at this.
Thief Nora: T-This is a human bone, right!?

Priestess Sophia: The fact that you went out of your way to
show us this means that it's a special human bone... Is that
correct?

Researcher Dokusa: I believe I mentioned that I am
conducting research on the corpse of the dragon you
defeated.

Researcher Dokusa: While conducting my usual research, I
confirmed that a part of the dragon's bone had transformed
into human bone.
Mage Relm: It's not like it was found inside the body...

Researcher Dokusa: And also, I want you to take a look at
this.

Mage Relm: It's called a vessel. It may not be as powerful
as a crystal, but it can hold magic.

Mage Relm: By the way, it has a quite unique shape, doesn't
it?

Researcher Dokusa: According to Karos, it seems to resemble
something from the neighboring country of Tarasa.

Researcher Dokusa: I'm about to share a quite bold
hypothesis.

Researcher Dokusa: The dragon is an artificial creation made
by someone!

Mage Relm: That's ridiculous! The grimoire that can create
dragons has been lost--

Mage Relm: Indeed, while it may not exist in the Empire, it
might exist in Tarasa...

Researcher Dokusa: I have also reached the same possibility,
so the next dragon might be born.

Researcher Dokusa: If humans are being used as materials for
the dragons, there is a high possibility that they are
utilizing powerful mages with high magical abilities.

Priestess Sophia: Could it be that the request is about
searching for a mage?

Researcher Dokusa: Our friend Parad, who is the owner of
this house, has gone missing. I've also heard rumors of
other mages disappearing.

Researcher Dokusa: In the last letter, the location was
written. I would like you to go to the Great Hole of the
Pharmacist in my place and search.
Clea: Understood, I will accept the request.

Researcher Dokusa: I feel like this investigation on dragons
is the entrance to some major incident.
Researcher Dokusa: ...Please be careful as well.

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Oros Region/Pharmacist's Great
Hole\c[0]
